Package labb5.simulation.supermarket.state.utilities

Class FIFO

java.lang.Object
labb5.simulation.supermarket.state.utilities.FIFO
public class FIFO extends Object
Describes the queue that appears when there are more people waiting to make their purchases than there are available registers in the supermarket simulator All the registers share a common queue.
Author:
Arvid From, Stefan Jonsson, Dino Lolic, William Kiwanuka
